Group Resist Magic = lvl 49 enchanter spell<br>
<br>
50 = Arcane quill (Casts Elemental Armor)<br>
Elemental Armor = lvl 44 wizard spell<br>
<br>
51 = Gem of Flowing Breath (Casts Everlasting Breath)<br>
Everlasting Breath = lvl 51 enchanter spell<br>
<br>
